Cineworld, Odeon Targeted by BC Partners, Mail on Sunday Says

-- B y   B e n   F a r e y
-- 
2011-02-20T14:50:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-20/cineworld-odeon-targeted-by-bc-partners-mail-on-sunday-says.html
  BC Partners  Ltd., a private equity
firm, may have made takeover approaches to Cineworld Group Plc
and Odeon Cinema Holdings Ltd., the  Mail on Sunday  reported.  Neither company is up for sale, the newspaper said, though
they are said to be open to approaches, it reported without
saying where it got its information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
